# Ephemeral loop runtime artifacts — regenerated by lib/ scripts each run.
# The durable record is loop.json, STATUS.md, and the per-round *.md artifacts.
env-capabilities.json
ac-results-R*.json
.vitest-results.json
# Atomic-write temp file for loop.json (renamed into place; a leftover means
# a crash mid-write — loop.json itself is always the last good state).
loop.json.tmp
